description:
Ana Foxxx has been impressive this season. She's got all the makings of a superstar for Ultimate Surrender. She's got long strong legs and a statuesque physique. Once she has control of her opponent, she takes full advantage. Her weakness, however, is she lets go of control from some unknown reason. We think its her way of playing cat and mouse.
Milcah Halili is new to the US mats. She does have some wrestling experience, however. She's a scrappy girl who refuses to lose to an amateur. Both girls put their hearts into this war. Both struggle to impose their sexually dominant will onto each other. Only one can come up on top. Winner fucks loser in a brutal fashion, using the loser's face as a sex toy.
title: Two exotic wrestlers struggle on the mats for sexual supremacy
